data.description: The perfect edge of town location with a brick ranch 3 bedroom home at this price? Yes please! Full unfinished (but nice) basement, comfortable room sizes and a huge yard right at the brink of town's end means convenience and privacy all at once. Sold as is- cash or conventional buyers only. Most buyers may want some cosmetic changes but overall a great home!
